  "title": "ImpellerType",
  "description": "A Thing Model of an OPC UA ObjectType showing type, reference and modelling-rule mappings: subtype extension, contained-in composition, congruent type identity, forward and inverse HasComponent references, a typed reference, a HasOrderedComponent subtype pinned by a typed link, and the four modelling-rule values.",
  "uav:browseName": "1:ImpellerType",
  "uav:id": "nsu=http://example.com/demo/pump;i=1005",
  "uav:containedIn": "PumpType",
